<subSubSection pageId="23" pageNumber="618" type="conservation">
<paragraph blockId="23.[1433,2640,2735,3476]" pageId="23" pageNumber="618">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[1435,1783,3247,3280]" pageId="23" pageNumber="618">Status and Conservation.</emphasis>
Classified as Data Deficient on The IUCN Red List. The Smalltoothed Mole occurs in two isolated distributions in Central Highlands and southern Vietnam and is poorly known.
</paragraph>
